quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  54,9,"Asanadze iwo, anthu a Nowa adakana kapolo wathu ndipo adati, “Uyu ndi munthu wamisala.” Ndipo iwo adamuthamangitsa iye ndi kumunyoza kwambiri"
  54,10,"Ndipo iye adadandaula kwa Ambuye wake nati, “Ndagonjetsedwa kotero idzani kuti mundithandize.”"
  54,11,"Motero Ife tidatsekula makomo a kumwamba, ndipo mvula idagwa nthawi yomweyo"
  54,12,Ndipo tidatumphutsa a kasupe padziko lapansi kotero madzi onse adakumana monga mwa lamulo lathu
  54,13,Ndipo tidamunyamula iye m’chombo chopangidwandimatabwandichokhomedwandimisomali
  54,14,Chidanyamuka potsogozedwa ndi Ife. Mphotho kwa iye amene adakanidwa
  54,15,Ndithudi tidachisiya icho ngati chizindikiro koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,16,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zalikulu bwanji
  54,17,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulidziwa ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,18,Anthu a Aad adakana. Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,19,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza mphepo yamkhuntho pa tsiku latsoka losasimbika
  54,20,Kugwetsa anthu ngati kuti adali mathunthu a mitengo ya mgwalangwa yozulidwa
  54,21,Kodi chilango changa ndipo chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,22,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,23,Anthu a Thamoud adakana machenjezo
  54,24,"Iwo adati, “Munthu! Mmodzi yekha wochokera ku mtundu wathu kuti timutsatire? Ndithudi ife tikhala olakwa kwambiri ndiponso a misala.”"
  54,25,“Kodi ndiye kuti uthenga waperekedwa kwa iye yekha pakati pa ife tonse? Iyayi! Iye ndi wabodza ndi wodzikweza.”
  54,26,Mawa iwo adzadziwa kuti wabodza ndi wodzikweza ndani
  54,27,Ndithudi Ife titumiza ngamira yaikazi ngati mayesero kwa iwo. Motero iwe uwapenyetsetse ndipo ukhale wopirira
  54,28,Ndipo uwauze kuti azigawana madzi. Ndipo nthawi yomwera madzi idzakhazikitsidwa
  54,29,Ndipo iwo adaitana m’bale wawo ndipo iye adatulutsa lupanga ndi kuipha
  54,30,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,31,Ndithudi tidawatumizira mfuwu umodzi ndipo onse adali ngati nkhuni zodula zimene munthu womanga mpanda amatola
  54,32,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,33,Anthu a Loti adati chenjezo lathu ndi labodza
  54,34,Ndithudi Ife tidawatumizira mphepo yonyamula miyala kupatula a pa banja la Loti amene tidawapulumutsa mu ola lomaliza la usiku
  54,35,"Monga chisomo chochokera kwa Ife, motero ndi mmene timalipirira anthu oyamika"
  54,36,Ndithudi iye adawachenjeza za chilango chathu choopsa koma iwo adakana chenjezo lathu
  54,37,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo adafuna kuchititsa manyazi alendo ake. Motero Ife tidawachititsa khungu. Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga"
  54,38,Ndithudi chilango chowawa chidadza pa iwo nthawi yam’mawa
  54,39,Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga
  54,40,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,41,"Ndipo, ndithudi, machenjezo adadza kwa anthu a Farawo"
  54,42,Iwo adati machenjezo athu onse ndi abodza motero tidawaononga ndi chilango champhamvu yochuluka
  54,43,Kodi anthu anu osakhulupirira ndi abwino kuposa awa? Kapena inu muli ndi chitetezo mu m’mawu a Mulungu
  54,44,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Ife ndife ambiri ndipo tidzapambana?”"
  54,45,Tsopano magulu awo ali kupirikitsidwa ndipo iwo ali kuthawa
  54,46,"Iyayi, koma ola lachiweruzo ndi nthawi imene iwo adalonjezedwa ndipo ola limeneli lidzakhala loopsa kwambiri"
  54,47,Ndithudi anthu osakhulupirira ndi olakwa adzapsya
  54,48,"Tsiku limene iwo adzaduduluzidwa pa nkhope zawo kunka ku moto, (zidzanenedwa) “Lawani ululu wa ku Moto.”"
  54,49,Ndithudi tidalenga chilichonse molingana ndi muyeso wake
  54,50,Ndipo ulamuliro wathu ndi umodzi monga kuphenira kwa diso
  54,51,Ndithudi Ife tidaononga kale anthu onga inu koma kodi alipo amene anga chenjezedwe
  54,52,Ndipo zonse zimene adachita zidalembedwa
  54,53,Ndipo chilichonse chaching’ono ndi chachikulu chidalembedwa kale
  54,54,Ndithudi onse amene amalewa zoipa adzakhala m’kati mwa minda ndi mitsinje
  54,55,Ku Paradiso kufupi ndi Mfumu yamphamvu zonse